thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Mike Wilkerson

author: Mike Wilkerson
title: Mike Wilkerson
text: Haven't received my first box yet but Taylor helped me out on an issue I had when when subscribing my first time. I chose the wrong subscription so she refunded the money and got me on the right subscription I wanted and made sure I would still receive a box in march! Looking forward to my first Lucky Tackle Box!
